title: Israeli President Isaac Herzog's Visit Disrupted Amid Melbourne Protests | 10 News
description: Israeli President Isaac Herzog has visited Melbourne today, in the final stop of his controversial visit to Australia.  He was due to visit the Adass Israel Synagogue at Ripponlea this morning but, was forced to ditch plans at the last minute because of safety fears as anger mounted in the city.
